greek life stanford recruitment guide 2011 welcome and thank you for your interest in the greek community here at stanford whether you already intend to join a greek organization or are sitting on the fence this guide will provide you with helpful information that you will need to make an informed choice that's right for you stanford's greek community consists of a wide variety of organizations with different interests goals and characteristics the links below are provided by the four greek governing organizations and include information about each group's activities and policies for prospective new members african american fraternal sororal association fraternities and sororities interfraternity council fraternities only intersorority council sororities only multicultural greek council fraternities and sororities if you do choose to embark on the journey of becoming a member of a greek organization below you will find some helpful tools glossary greek alphabet stanford fraternity and soroity life is a part of residential education
